
taxonomia.php
=============

This is a utility for exploring a local document repository.

REQUIREMENTS
------------

- php 5.5 with following extensions
   - pdo
   - dba
composer
curl
make
git
python2.7

INSTALL
-------

Use composer for installing dependencies.

Edit app/src/settings.php so that shelf rootdir points to folder
where your documents are stored.

Run scripts indexer.

Start server.sh and look what is already done.

Thank you for using taxonomia.php.
